
# 🚀 ThriveX AI Mentor

ThriveX is an AI-powered voice mentor app built with Streamlit. It listens to your voice, detects your emotional tone, and provides motivational advice in real time.

## 🎯 Features
- 🎙️ Upload your voice (WAV/MP3)
- 🧠 AI-powered emotion analysis (mocked for now)
- 💬 ChatGPT (GPT-4 Turbo) motivational coaching
- ☁️ Deployed on Streamlit Cloud

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python + Streamlit
- OpenAI API (GPT-4 Turbo)
- Whisper API (for transcription)
- TensorFlow (optional for emotion model)
- Deployed on Streamlit Cloud

## 🚀 Getting Started
Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Thrivex1123/ThriveX-AI-Mentor
cd ThriveX-AI-Mentor
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
